{"id":"api/common/getNumberOfCurrencyDigits","title":"getNumberOfCurrencyDigits","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/getNumberOfCurrencyDigits\", \"name\": \"getNumberOfCurrencyDigits\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/i18n/locale_data_api.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1088-L1116\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/common/src/i18n/locale_data_api.ts#L1088-L1116\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"getnumberofcurrencydigits\">getNumberOfCurrencyDigits<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/getNumberOfCurrencyDigits#getnumberofcurrencydigits\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">報告給定貨幣的小數位數。其值取決於該特定貨幣中分幣是否存在。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Reports the number of decimal digits for a given currency.\nThe value depends upon the presence of cents in that particular currency.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/common/getNumberOfCurrencyDigits\" class=\"code-anchor\">getNumberOfCurrencyDigits</a></span>(code: string): number</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"引數\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>code</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">貨幣程式碼。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The currency code.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">小數位數，通常為 0 或 2。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>number</code>: The number of decimal digits, typically 0 or 2.</p>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/getNumberOfCurrencyDigits#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-overview\">國際化(i18n)指南</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"https://angular.io/guide/i18n-overview\">Internationalization (i18n) Guide</a></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/getNumberOfCurrencyDigits#getnumberofcurrencydigits\n - api/common/getNumberOfCurrencyDigits#see-also\n - guide/i18n-overview\n - https://angular.io/guide/i18n-overview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/i18n/locale_data_api.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1088-L1116\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/common/src/i18n/locale_data_api.ts#L1088-L1116\n-->"}